headline: Here's Why MarketAxess (MKTX) Could be Great Choice for a Bottom Fisher
summary: MarketAxess (MKTX) witnesses a hammer chart pattern, indicating support found by the stock after losing some value lately. This coupled with an upward trend in earnings estimate revisions could mean a trend reversal for the stock in the near term.

headline: Royce Global Financial Services Fund Q3 2024 Commentary
summary: Royce Global Financial Services Fund advanced 7.6% for the quarter, outperforming its benchmark, MSCI ACWI Small Cap Index, which was up 3.9% for the same period.
